                s
              
              thresholds maps sensing into logic functions, enabling reconfigurable operation () and a three‐input {AND} gate at room temperature. Grounded in the fundamentals of the {CISS} effect, this adaptive approach paves the way for spin‐logic as a reliable platform for molecular‐scale information processing, intelligent diagnostics, and future reconfigurable spintronic technologies.},
